    <h2>About Us</h2>
    <p>If you want to enjoy authentic Chinese, North Indian, Continental or Italian cuisine, The Bikerâ€™s Cafe at Golf Course Road in Gurgaon would be an ideal option. Nice subtle decor along with Live screening of the matches, the place is hot favourite with the youngsters. It is a neat and cozy restaurant. The ambience of the place is nice and the nice numbers are being placed all the time.

        Some of the signature dishes here are Indian Tandoori platter, Cottage Cheese Lasooni Palak Spring Rolls, Rajma Gaulati Kebab, Chilli Chicken, Kung Pao Tofu, Daal Makhani, Highway Curry, Tawa Chicken, Palak Paneer and different Pizzas with variety of toppings. The meat dishes have adequate meat and have rich aromatic flavors. The gigantic piece of Naan with Delhi 6 Curry is simply incredible. Monthly specials make the place interesting for the guests. The Indian Kababs served here are quite different. Variety of cocktail drinks and fresh Brewed Beer is the highlight of this place.</p>
